eft-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1eabu CH Czech Alena Seredova chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 khi c\u00f4 bi\u1ebft ch\u1ed3ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Buffon ngo\u1ea1i t\u00ecnh g\u1ea7n 4 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1ecbp sinh nh\u1eadt l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 40, Alena Seredova c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n v\u1edbi b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italy, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f4 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Buffon, ng\u01b0\u1eddi chung s\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng c\u00f4 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2011-2014 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 v\u1edbi nhau hai \u0111\u1ee9a con. Theo nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a Alena Seredova v\u1edbi t\u1ea1p ch\u00ed Chi, c\u00f4 ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng chung th\u1ee7y c\u1ee7a Buffon t\u1eeb b\u00e1o ch\u00ed.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Vo cu ke lai cam giac bi thu mon Buffon phan boi hinh anh\" title=\"V\u1ee3 c\u0169 k\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c b\u1ecb th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Buffon ph\u1ea3n b\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/cc-2890-1522288145.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Buffon v\u00e0 Alena Seredova c\u00f3 4 n\u0103m l\u00e0m v\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng. \u1ea2nh: NS.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\"T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n k\u1ebft th\u00fac cu\u1ed9c h\u00f4n nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh theo m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ecdc th\u00f4ng tin t\u1eeb c\u00e1c t\u1edd b\u00e1o\", ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef 40 tu\u1ed5i chia s\u1ebb. Khi \u0111\u00f3, Alena Seredova ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n im l\u1eb7ng b\u1edfi theo c\u00f4, ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch hay kh\u00f3c l\u00f3c \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch h\u1ee3p. Ch\u00e2n d\u00e0i CH Czech quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chia tay th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Italy trong y\u00ean l\u1eb7ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u0103m 2014, Buffon tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ec1 t\u00e0i n\u00f3ng, lu\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean trang nh\u1ea5t c\u00e1c t\u1edd b\u00e1o khi b\u1ecb b\u1eaft g\u1eb7p ngo\u1ea1i t\u00ecnh. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u c\u1ee7a Juventus l\u00e9n l\u00fat quan h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi n\u1eef nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o Ilaria D'Amico.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Alena Seredova duy tr\u00ec m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m v\u1edbi Alessandro Nasi, ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eeba k\u1ebf c\u1ee7a d\u00f2ng h\u1ecd Agnelli gi\u00e0u c\u00f3. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Buffon c\u0169ng \u0111ang say \u0111\u1eafm v\u1edbi Ilaria D'Amico.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0i th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Alena Seredova c\u0169ng chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italy v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch c\u00f4 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng t\u00e2m l\u00fd. \"Kh\u00f4ng ai ch\u1ebft v\u00ec b\u1ecb c\u1eafm s\u1eebng c\u1ea3. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c s\u1ed1ng, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3\", ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb9p th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd khi tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo ngoisao.net<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"593","checkdouble":"183058"},{"date":"14:45 29/03","title":"B\u1ecb \u2018ch\u1eb7t ch\u00e9m\u2019 trong ... t\u00f9, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Tevez ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 1 th\u00e1ng","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/29/bi-chat-chem-trong-tu-tien-dao-tevez-phai-nghi-1-thang.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"592","checkdouble":"183059"},{"date":"14:48 29/03","title":"\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Lazio b\u1ecb hacker cu\u1ed7m 2 tri\u1ec7u euro ti\u1ec1n mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/29/doi-bong-lazio-bi-hacker-cuom-2-trieu-euro-tien-mua-cau-thu.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radiu