ius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lazio \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb nh\u1eefng hacker cu\u1ed7m 2 tri\u1ec7u euro ti\u1ec1n h\u1ecd n\u1ee3 Feyenoord \u1edf v\u1ee5 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Stefan de Vrij.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nTheo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Lazio \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t e-mail y\u00eau c\u1ea7u thanh to\u00e1n n\u1ed1t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n 2 tri\u1ec7u euro \u1edf v\u1ee5 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 De Vrij. \u0110\u00e1ng n\u00f3i \u1edf ch\u1ed7, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Olimpico ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n t\u01b0\u1edfng e-mail \u1ea5y l\u00e0 do ph\u00eda Feyenoord g\u1eedi, b\u1edfi c\u00f3 h\u1eb3n logo c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch vi\u1ebft gi\u1ed1ng h\u1ec7t.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/lazio.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nLazio \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec e-mail y\u00eau c\u1ea7u. Tuy nhi\u00ean, sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Serie A m\u1edbi ng\u00e3 ng\u1eeda khi bi\u1ebft Feyenoord ch\u01b0a h\u1ec1 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u1ea3n ph\u00ed n\u00e0o, v\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 2 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u00e3 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o tay m\u1ed9t nh\u00f3m hacker.\u00a0 <br />\r\n<br />\r\nS\u1edf d\u0129 Lazio bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0 do h\u1ecd th\u1ea5y s\u1ed1 IBAN (s\u1ed1 t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn ti\u1ec1n tr\u00ean ph\u1ea1m vi qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf) \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb thay \u0111\u1ed5i. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nNgay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1 vi\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111i\u1ec1u tra, v\u00e0 l\u1ea7n ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111ang n\u1eb1m trong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng \u1edf H\u00e0 Lan. <br />\r\n\u00a0<br />\r\nDe Vrij gia nh\u1eadp Lazio t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2014, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ebd ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng t\u1ef1 do v\u00e0o H\u00e8 2018 v\u00ec h\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi CLB.<br />\r\n\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"591","checkdouble":"183060"},{"date":"15:17 29/03","title":"5 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n hot nh\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/29/5-thu-mon-hot-nhat-ky-chuyen-nhuong-he-2018.png","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}