et-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua Top 5 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n hot nh\u1ea5t H\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alisson</h2>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nC\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i: AS Roma</h2>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Alisson: Liverpool, Arsenal, Real Madrd</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAlisson \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed5i l\u00ean nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t Serie A \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 trong khung g\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/roma-57.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Roma</strong></span>, c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a \u0110TQG Brazil, m\u1eb7c cho Selecao hi\u1ec7n gi\u1edd c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi Ederson c\u1ee7a Man City. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi 25 tu\u1ed5i s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. Alisson c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u1eb1ng ch\u00e2n c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"5 thu mon hot nhat ky chuyen nhuong He 2018 hinh anh\" title=\"5 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n hot nh\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/5-thu-mon-hot-nhat-ky-chuyen-nhuong-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Alisson</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u1ede Serie A m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Pepe Reina c\u1ee7a Napoli (15) gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n Alisson (13). Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Gianluigi Buffon c\u1ee7a Juventus n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Roma: &ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n \u0111em l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m tin cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng&rdquo;. H\u00e8 2016, AS Roma ch\u1ec9 m\u1ea5t 7,5 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu Alisson t\u1eeb Internacional, nh\u01b0ng l\u00fac n\u00e0y h\u1ecd \u0111ang \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ebfn 80 tri\u1ec7u euro cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Jan Oblak</h2>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nCLB hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i: Atletico Madrid</h2>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Jan Oblak: Chelsea, Arsenal, MU</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau khi Thibaut Courtois tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea, Jan Oblak v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn thay th\u1ebf. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn nay anh lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u trong khung g\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Slovenia l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ch\u01a1i \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1ea5t La Liga trong 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, Oblak \u0111ang ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, gi\u00fap Atletico ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn 14 b\u00e0n thua sau 29 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf La Liga.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jan Oblak\" title=\"Jan Oblak\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/oblak.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jan Oblak</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nJan Oblak c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 v\u00e0 b\u1eaft b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. M\u00f9a n\u00e0y anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 2/3 qu\u1ea3 11m \u1edf La Liga. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 khi\u1ebfn anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, Atletico kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh n\u1ebfu thu v\u1ec1 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 70 tri\u1ec7u euro. Khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft nh\u1eefng g\u00ec x\u1ea3y ra v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y mai, h\u00f4m nay t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Atletico, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u1eady th\u00f4i&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Timo Horn</h2>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nCLB hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i: Cologne</h2>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Timo Horn: Arsenal</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTimo Horn \u0111ang l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Cologne, c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf Bundesliga m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, thu\u1ed9c Top 3 (74 l\u1ea7n), trung b\u00ecnh 2,8 l\u1ea7n/tr\u1eadn. V\u1edbi chi\u1ec1u cao 1m92 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i b\u1eaft b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 c\u1ee7a anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Timo Horn\" title=\"Timo Horn\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/horn.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Timo Horn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 Timo Horn \u0111ang ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng Cologne l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ea3i xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng. H\u1ecd \u0111ang x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 17 tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng Bundesliga, k\u00e9m nh\u00f3m an to\u00e0n 5 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 7 v\u00f2ng. N\u1ebfu Cologne xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i chi ra 5,4 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Arsenal \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i thay Petr Cech, h\u1ecd \u0111ang r\u1ed9ng c\u1eeda chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf k\u1ef3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/tin-chuyen-nhuong-c187-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng</strong></span> H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2><strong>Kepa Arrizabalaga</strong></h2>\r\n<h2><strong><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i: Athletic Bilbao</strong></h2>\r\n<h2><strong><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Kepa Arrizabalaga: Real Madrid, Chelsea</strong></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKepa Arrizabalaga \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u1edf La Liga m\u00f9a n\u00e0y khi ch\u01a1i \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Athletic Bilbao. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha gi\u1ecfi b\u1eaft b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng, c\u00f2n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u1edf c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng d\u00e0i c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, Arrizabalaga c\u00f3 6 l\u1ea7n gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf La Liga v\u00e0 63 l\u1ea7n c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1. Trung b\u00ecnh anh c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 2,42 l\u1ea7n/tr\u1eadn, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 Keylor Navas (2,24 l\u1ea7n/tr\u1eadn) c\u1ee7a Real Madrid.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kepa Arrizabalaga\" title=\"Kepa Arrizabalaga\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/kepa.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kepa Arrizabalaga</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nReal Madrid \u0111ang quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 30 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Chelsea c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994. Khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh Kepa Arrizabalaga kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: &ldquo;T\u00f4i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh y\u00eau r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Bilbao, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y c\u00e0ng l\u00e2u c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Bernd Leno</h2>\r\n<h2><br>\r\n<strong>CLB hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i: Bayer Leverkusen</strong></h2>\r\n<h2><br>\r\n<strong>Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Bernd Leno: Arsenal, Napoli, Real Madrid</strong></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBernd Leno l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ch\u01a1i \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1ea5t Bundesliga trong 5 n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. T\u00ednh t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2011/12, anh l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f3 s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u cao nh\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u1ee9c (227 l\u1ea7n). C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Bundesliga v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch m\u1ed9t trong 3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f3 3 l\u1ea7n gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp khi ra m\u1eaft. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Bayer Leverkusen \u0111ang ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi 8 l\u1ea7n gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi sau 27 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Bundesliga.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bernd Leno\" title=\"Bernd Leno\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/leno.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bernd Leno</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nS\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Bernd Leno khi\u1ebfn anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 theo d\u00f5i t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/arsenal-4.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Arsenal</strong></span> \u0111ang nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i thay Petr Cech, Napoli v\u00e0 Real c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992. 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Bayer Leverkusen nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Leno c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018: &ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft nh\u1eefng g\u00ec s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Th\u1eadt vinh d\u1ef1 khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn quan t\u00e2m, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd suy ngh\u0129 n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"590","checkdouble":"183064"},{"date":"15:35 29/03","title":"HLV Anh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o su\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 World Cup cho sao Tottenham","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/29/hlv-southgate-khong-chac-dele-alli-du-world-cup-cung-dt-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.artic