></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Gareth Southgate kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc r\u1eb1ng c\u00f3 mang ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Tottenham t\u1edbi World Cup 2018 hay kh\u00f4ng.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 sa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/dele-alli-gioi-nhat-the-gioi-o-tuoi-21-172-182174.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Dele Alli t\u1ea1i Tottenham</strong></span>. H\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 21 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ea1i \u0110T Anh tham d\u1ef1 VCK World Cup 2018 t\u1ea1i Nga. HLV Gareth Southgate m\u1edbi ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ch\u1ed7 cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 v\u00e0 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ea3i \u00f4m h\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSo v\u1edbi 2 m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Dele Alli hi\u1ec7n suy gi\u1ea3m v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9. Con s\u1ed1 ch\u1ec9 10 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 42 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u00f9a n\u00e0y ch\u01b0a h\u1eb3n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t y\u00eau c\u1ea7u. \u0110\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do trong \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1eadp trung th\u00e1ng 3 n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh, Alli ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n \u1edf ph\u00fat 68 c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 Lan v\u00e0 ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1 v\u1edbi Italia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Southgate khong chac Dele Alli du World Cup cung DT Anh hinh anh\" title=\"HLV Southgate kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc Dele Alli d\u1ef1 World Cup c\u00f9ng \u0110T Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/18/HLV-Southgate-khong-chac-Dele-Alli-du-World-Cup-cung-DT-Anh-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Dele Alli \u0111ang tr\u1ea3i qua m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 mong \u0111\u1ee3i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Dele Alli d\u1ef1 World Cup c\u00f9ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/adam-lallana-da-san-sang-thach-thuc-tat-ca-172-183046.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>\u0110T Anh</strong></span> ch\u01b0a th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng. Ch\u00ednh HLV Gareth Southgate trong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn trong tay \u00f4ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 t\u1eeb Marcus Rashford, Jesse Lingard, Raheem Sterling, Harry Kane, Alex Oxlade-Chamberlain t\u1edbi Jamie Vardy\u2026 V\u00f4 s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn trong tay\u201d, Southgate n\u00f3i. \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t nh\u00e2n t\u00e0i n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng d\u1ef1 World Cup t\u1ea1i Nga.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Gareth Southgate dang gay an tuong rat lon\" title=\"HLV Gareth Southgate \u0111ang g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/28/HLV.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV Southgate kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc Dele Alli d\u1ef1 World Cup c\u00f9ng \u0110T Anh</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00f3. V\u1edbi th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Dele Alli \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ebfn World Cup v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng to l\u1edbn \u1edf \u0111\u00f3. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 t\u00e0i v\u00e0 t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i c\u1eadu \u1ea5y trong v\u00e0i tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede VCK World Cup 2018, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/dt-anh-tra-gia-dat-sau-chien-thang-truoc-ha-lan-172-182747.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>\u0110T Anh</strong></span> n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng G c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi B\u1ec9, Panama v\u00e0 Tunisia. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n v\u1edbi Tunisia v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam ng\u00e0y 18/6 t\u1edbi, Tam s\u01b0 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 2 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi Nigeria v\u00e0 Costa Rica l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t c\u00e1c ng\u00e0y 2 v\u00e0 7 th\u00e1ng 6 t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/adam-lallana-da-san-sang-thach-thuc-tat-ca-172-183046.html\">Adam Lallana \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bonucci-nhung-cau-thu-tre-cua-dt-anh-con-manh-hon-tuyen-y-421-182926.html\">Bonucci: Nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh c\u00f2n m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n tuy\u1ec3n \u00dd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sterling-muon-duoc-yeu-thuong-o-dt-anh-421-182925.html\">Sterling mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf \u0110T Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/dt-anh-tra-gia-dat-sau-chien-thang-truoc-ha-lan-172-182747.html\">\u0110T Anh tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 Lan</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-tuc-world-cup/southgate-hai-long-voi-tinh-than-thi-dau-cua-dt-anh-439-182719.html\">Southgate h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"589","checkdouble":"183062"},{"date":"15:36 29/03","title":"D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y Martial s\u1ebd r\u1eddi MU h\u00e8 n\u00e0y","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2017/12/2/dau-hieu-cho-thay-martial-se-roi-mu-he-nay.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-in