ound:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd, Martial \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Blaise Matuidi v\u1ec1 mong mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi MU v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Juventus \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Dau hieu cho thay Martial roi MU he nay hinh anh\" title=\"D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y Martial r\u1eddi MU h\u00e8 n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/12/Dau-hieu-cho-thay-Martial-roi-MU-he-nay-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Martial c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi MU v\u00e0o h\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Martial \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 3 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Man United. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111e d\u1ecda nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng v\u00ec s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Alexis Sanchez \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 t\u1edbi, Martial s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. D\u00f9 ph\u00eda Man United c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gia h\u1ea1n th\u00eam 1 n\u0103m n\u1eefa nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 r\u1ebb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ph\u00eda Man United hy v\u1ecdng Martial s\u1ebd k\u00fd v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. Nh\u01b0ng t\u1edd Tuttosport m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0a tin r\u1eb1ng Juventus \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Martial g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u201cL\u00e3o b\u00e0\u201d t\u1edbi Anh l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Tottenham trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 v\u00f2ng 1/8 Champions League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb Tuttosport c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng s\u1ee9c h\u00fat c\u1ee7a Juventus \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ea7n d\u1ea7n \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi Martial. Trong \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1eadp trung \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia v\u1eeba qua, nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n gi\u1eefa Martial v\u00e0 Matuidi g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1ec9 xoay quanh cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng t\u1ea1i Juventus.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHai gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Fabio Paratici v\u00e0 Beppe Marotta \u0111\u00e3 theo d\u00f5i Martial t\u1eeb khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f2n ch\u01a1i cho Lyon. V\u00e0 \u201cL\u00e3o b\u00e0\u201d \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Martial tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ecb Man United cu\u1ed7m m\u1ea5t v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2015.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-dung-luong-sieu-khung-du-ronaldo-tro-lai-old-trafford-172-183045.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/19/mu-dung-luong-sieu-khung-du-ronaldo-tro-lai-old-trafford.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-dung-luong-sieu-khung-du-ronaldo-tro-lai-old-trafford-172-183045.html\">M.U d\u00f9ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng d\u1ee5 Ronaldo tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford</span><br>\r\n<span>Theo Diario Gol, BL\u0110 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i MU \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Martial g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i cam k\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai l\u00e2u d\u00e0i v\u1edbi Man United. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u khi t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb gi\u1ea3m b\u1edbt \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Manchester qua m\u00f9a h\u00e8 kh\u00f4ng \u01b0? T\u00f4i xin l\u1ed7i nh\u01b0ng \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i g\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\u201d, Philippe Lamboley chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi t\u1edd iBiancoNero h\u1ed3i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i kh\u00f4n ngoan v\u1edbi Martial. S\u00e2n Juventus Arena th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 n\u01a1i ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng. Tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Paul Pogba tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 minh ch\u1ee9ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng nh\u1ea5t cho kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng n\u00e2ng \u0111\u1ee1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Bianconeri.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (Bongda24h)</strong></div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"588","checkdouble":"183063"},{"date":"10:43 29/03","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/6/16/day-thu-mon-moi-nhat-lot-vao-tam-ngam-cua-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articler