Madrid mua Gianluigi Donnarumma c\u1ee7a AC Milan, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn Los Blancos.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</h2>\r\n<h2>Real Madrid r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Keylor Navas v\u1eabn ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1eafp b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 32, kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady anh kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao tr\u1ebb h\u01a1n v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gap kho vu De Gea, Real Madrid mua Gianluigi Donnarumma hinh anh\" title=\"G\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 v\u1ee5 De Gea, Real Madrid mua Gianluigi Donnarumma h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/21/Gap-kho-vu-De-Gea,-Real-Madrid-mua-Gianluigi-Donnarumma-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real c\u1ea7n ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay Keylor Navas</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nHi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Los Blancos \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-mua-thu-mon-moi-thay-cho-de-gea-courtois-180-181599.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Real quan t\u00e2m Bernd Leno</strong></span> c\u1ee7a Bayer Leverkusen, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1o ch\u00ed \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i. Song 2 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd v\u1eabn l\u00e0 Courtois c\u1ee7a Chelsea v\u00e0 David de Gea c\u1ee7a M.U.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Real chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Courtois ho\u1eb7c De Gea \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. M.U v\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi hai trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/real-madrid-29.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Real</strong></span> c\u00f3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn th\u00ec kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 Courtois hay De Gea v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Song song v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t trong hai th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y, Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Gianluigi Donnarumma l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Don Balon, Real Madrid mua Gianluigi Donnarumma c\u1ee7a AC Milan \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Los Blancos. HLV Zidane v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez \u0111\u1ec1u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Bernabeu.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool mua Gianluigi Donnarumma\" title=\"Liverpool mua Gianluigi Donnarumma\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/28/nguoi-cu-muon-liverpool-mua-thu-mon-cua-ac-milan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real Madrid mua Gianluigi Donnarumma</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nDonnarumma \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tr\u1ebb xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, anh \u0111ang l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a AC Milan. \u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Real ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 50 tri\u1ec7u euro. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Real Madrid mua Gianluigi Donnarumma th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1edfi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 19 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi San Siro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Real th\u00ec <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nguoi-cu-muon-liverpool-mua-thu-mon-cua-ac-milan-172-183013.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Liverpool c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m Donnarumma</strong></span>, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 c\u1ee7a The Kop l\u00e0 Steve Nicol \u0111\u00e3 khuy\u00ean L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a AC Milan. Nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng so v\u1ec1 s\u1ee9c h\u00fat v\u00e0 t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh, Real v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n Liverpool trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Gianluigi Donnarumma \u1edf Serie A 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/756514-42720/033100\" target=\"_blank\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Gianluigi Donnarumma \u1edf Serie A 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"587","checkdouble":"183050"},{"date":"11:10 29/03","title":"Arsenal v\u00e0 Real g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 v\u1ee5 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Atletico","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/29/arsenal-va-real-gap-kho-vu-hau-ve-cua-atletico.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding: